Each element of the array becomes one line of text, delimited by a NL char, in the os file.

Any existing os file is replaced.

\fBcodepage:\fR Optional: Data is converted from UTF8 to the required codepage/encoding before output. If the conversion cannot be performed then return false.

\fBReturns:\fR True if successful or false if not.


